---
description: VideoPlayer regression prevention
globs: ["study-desk/src/components/VideoPlayer.tsx"]
---

CRITICAL: The unmount cleanup in VideoPlayer MUST defer the onProgress call with setTimeout.
Synchronous state updates during unmount block React Router transitions (URL changes but content stays stuck).

```ts
// CORRECT — deferred
window.setTimeout(() => onProgress(finalPosition, finalDuration), 0)

// WRONG — synchronous, breaks navigation
onProgress(video.currentTime, video.duration)
```
